WEBVTT

00:00:02.643 --> 00:00:05.119
JR: Art is not supposed
to change the world.

00:00:05.143 --> 00:00:08.815
But art can change
the way we see the world.

00:00:08.839 --> 00:00:09.989
(Music)

00:00:15.640 --> 00:00:17.329
So now my wish is ...

00:00:19.196 --> 00:00:23.399
for you to stand up
for what you care about

00:00:24.469 --> 00:00:27.276
by participating in a global art project.